            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your<strong> ciabatta[s] </strong>in half</p><p>Spread the <strong>cheesy garlic butter</strong> over the outside of the<strong> ciabatta lids</strong> and the inside of the <strong>ciabatta</strong> <strong>bases</strong>, then add to a baking tray and put the tray in the oven for 5-7 min or until crusty – this is your<strong> garlic bread</strong></p><p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>mashed roasted garlic</strong>, <strong>mayo</strong> and the<strong> white wine vinegar </strong>in a small bowl – this is your <strong>roasted garlic aioli</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1643798623230-x200.jpg",
